'''Eternity Gaming''' is a European multi-gaming organization. Registered in the United Kingdom, its origins lie in Sarajevo, Bosnia and Herzegovina. The team was founded on the 1st April 2009 and started off as a collaboration between a few like-minded individuals. Eternity Gaming has now grown to include a number of divisions:
* StarCraft II
* League of Legends
* Counter Strike: Global Offensive

